title: What causes Obesity in Kiribati
summary: This chart shows the factors which Cause Obesity in Kiribati and the percentage of their contribution .

Fast_Food account for just under 25 percentage of Obesity , followed by Lack_of_Exercise of which accounts for 35 percentage of Obesity , but Genetic is the highest contributing factor accounting for 40.1 percentage of the Cause of Obesity .
gold: The causes of obesity in Kiribati are charted above to show that the predominant cause of obesity was found to be genetic at 40 % . Fast food was the lowest charted percentage at 24 % with lack of exercise only contributing 35 % towards the outcome .
